        <li>Order a beginner microphone</li>
        <li>Record your first episode (even if it's rough)</li>
        <li>Edit and upload to a host</li>
        <li>Submit to Apple Podcasts and Spotify</li>
        <li>Tell everyone you know</li>
      </ol>
